narrative.title: Provider Overview
narrative.text: Wind River Family & Community Healthc Care is a Clinic/Center  Public Health  Federal provider based in Arapahoe, WY. From the 2018–2024 period, this provider received $93.8M in Medicaid payments across 277K claims.

narrative.title: Why This Matters
narrative.text: At $93.8M in Medicaid payments, this provider represents significant public healthcare spending. Understanding where these dollars go helps ensure the program serves those who need it most.
